HEADWORD: Sizable
<hw>Siz"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of
considerable size or bulk.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>sizable</xex>
volume.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Bp. Hurd.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Being of reasonable or suitable size; <as>as,
